<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100766>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Habitus of Stenosagola species, dorsal view. a) Winged male of S. connata, b) Wingless male of S. connata, c) Female of S. connata, d) Winged male of S. huiaensis, e) Female of S. huiaensis, f) Winged male of S. northlandensis, g) Wingless male of S. northlandensis, h) Female of S. northlandensis, i) Winged male of S. thayerae, j) Wingless male of S. thayerae, k) Female of S. thayerae, l) Winged male of S. dugdalei, m) Wingless male of S. dugdalei. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100766/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100773>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Locations where Stenosagola connata triangles), Stenosagola huiaensis (circles), and Stenosagola northlandensis (squares) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
